'''{{ill|Nekozuka Kofun|ja|猫塚古墳}}''' (ねこづかこふん) is the name of multiple {{ill|Kofun|ja|古墳}} burial mounds in Japan.
* **{{ill|Nekozuka Kofun (Sendai)|ja|猫塚古墳 (仙台市)}}** ({{ill|Sendai|ja|仙台市}}, {{ill|Miyagi Prefecture|ja|宮城県}}) * **{{ill|Gojō Nekozuka Kofun|ja|五条猫塚古墳}}** ({{ill|Gojō, Nara|ja|五條市}}, {{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県}}) * **Nekozuka Kofun** ({{ill|Nara, Nara|ja|奈良市}}, {{ill|Nara Prefecture|ja|奈良県}}) * **Nekozuka Kofun** ({{ill|Takamatsu, Kagawa|ja|高松市}}, {{ill|Kagawa Prefecture|ja|香川県}}) → Part of **{{ill|Ishizuchi Kofun Cluster|ja|石清尾山古墳群}}** (a National Historic Site).
{{DEFAULTSORT:Nekozuka Kofun}} [[Category:Kofun in Japan]] {{Disambiguation}}

